ingredientsDesc:
Access BR Monitor Reagent :
R1a : Paramagnetic particles, coated with goat anti-biotin antibodies, biotinylated anti-CA 15-3 antigen mouse monoclonal antibodies, BSA.
R1b : Mouse monoclonal anti-CA 15-3 antigen-alkaline phosphates (bovine) conjugate, BSA.
R1c : Buffered protein solution (bovine, goat, mouse).
Access BR Monitor Calibrators : 
S0 : Buffered BSA.
S1，S2，S3，S4，S5：CA 15-3 antigen at levels of approximately 10, 50, 100, 500 and 1000 U/ml in buffered BSA.
Calibration Card：1
